rComments: this teacher makes this class way harder than it needs to be and consistently complains about us having "senioritis" or "spring fever" and on top of it all, he makes his class different than all of the others classes (harder)

Prof. Anderson is a great guy. He is energetic and keeps class interesting, although he does require constant class participation. He is a fair grader, and gives you clear guidelines on how to do well in his class.
